        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=You are an expert AI Job Matcher. Evaluate the job listing below against the candidate's profile. \nDo NOT assume any missing information. Your goal is to score the job out of a maximum of 5 points.\n\n### SCORING RULES (Maximum 5 Points)\n\n1. \"resume_match_score\" (0 to 3 points): \n   - 3: Perfect match. Strongly aligns with Backend, Cloud, or Distributed Systems. Uses Java, Python, AWS, or Docker.\n   - 2: Good match. Uses some of the tech stack but might be slightly broader (e.g., Full-stack with React/Spring Boot).\n   - 1: Partial match. Junior role but missing core cloud/backend focus.\n   - 0: Weak match. Completely different role (e.g., Data Science, purely frontend, HR).\n\n2. \"company_type_score\" (0 or 1 point): \n   - 1: Top Product Company, Tech Startup, or In-house Engineering team (e.g., Amazon, Swiggy, Emerson, Fintechs, SaaS).\n   - 0: Service-based company, IT Consulting, or Staffing Agency (e.g., Wipro, TCS, Infosys, Cognizant, Accenture, Tech Mahindra, staffing firms). If the description mentions \"working for our client\", score 0.\n\n3. \"employment_type_score\" (0 or 1 point): \n   - 1: Full-time role (If the employment type is not explicitly mentioned, assume 1).\n   - 0: Explicitly states \"Contract\", \"Internship\", \"Part-time\", or \"Freelance\".\n\n### CANDIDATE PROFILE (S Haswanth)\n- Target: Backend / Cloud / Distributed Systems Engineer.\n- Education: B.Tech CSE (2026), VIT Vellore.\n- Skills: Java, Python, C++, Spring Boot, React.js, AWS, Docker, Kubernetes, Terraform, SQL.\n- Experience/Projects: Distributed MLOps Framework, Property Insights Platform, System Design.\n\n### JOB LISTING TO EVALUATE\nTitle: {{ $json.title }}\nCompany: {{ $json.companyName }}\nLocation: {{ $json.location }}\nJob Description: {{ $json.descriptionText }}\n\n### OUTPUT INSTRUCTIONS\nYou must output ONLY a valid JSON object. Do NOT wrap the JSON in markdown formatting like ```json. Do NOT include any explanations, pleasantries, or extra text. Start your response immediately with the { character.\n\n{\n  \"resume_match_score\": 0,\n  \"company_type_score\": 0,\n  \"employment_type_score\": 0,\n  \"reasoning\": \"One short sentence explaining the score, specifically mentioning if it is a product vs service company and how the skills align.\"\n}"
            }
          ]
        },
        "simplify": false,
        "options": {}
      },
      "type": "@n8n/n8n-nodes-langchain.ollama",
