        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Task: Complete the 3-sentence LinkedIn cold message template below for the \"{{ $json.title }}\" role at \"{{ $json.companyName }}\".\n\nContext:\nJob Description: \"{{ $json.descriptionText }}\"\n\nMy Background: \nI build scalable systems using Java (Spring Boot), React, PostgreSQL, Docker, and Kubernetes.\n\nRules:\n1. Output EXACTLY 3 lines of text. \n2. Sentence 1 MUST be exactly this: \"Hi [Name], I'm an AWS Certified CS student (VIT '26) and I saw your opening for a {{ $json.title }}.\"\n3. Sentence 2: Write ONE sentence connecting a requirement from the Job Description to my experience with Java, React, or Docker/Kubernetes. Keep it under 15 words.\n4. Sentence 3 MUST be exactly this: \"Would you be open to reviewing my background or passing my resume to the hiring manager?\"\n5. Output ONLY the final 3-sentence message. Stop generating immediately after the third sentence."
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
