        "messages": {
          "values": [
            {
              "content": "=Task: Write a strictly formatted, 3-paragraph cold email to an Engineering Manager for the \"{{ $('Merge-company-Li').item.json.title }}\" role at \"{{ $('Merge-company-Li').item.json.companyName }}\".\n\nContext:\nJob Description: \"{{ $('Merge-company-Li').item.json.descriptionText }}\"\n\nMy Background:\nCS student at VIT (Class of '26), AWS Solutions Architect & IBM GenAI certified. Built a Java/Spring Boot Property Platform (<500ms latency), a distributed MLOps framework (Docker/Kubernetes), and a React AdTech Calculator.\n\nRules:\n1. Output EXACTLY 3 paragraphs using actual line breaks (press Enter between paragraphs). Do NOT output literal \"\\n\" characters. Do NOT format as JSON.\n2. Paragraph 1: Start with \"Hi [Name],\" followed by a maximum of 2 sentences mapping ONE requirement from the Job Description to my Java, React, or Docker/Kubernetes experience. \n3. Paragraph 2: MUST include this exact sentence: \"I am highly interested in this specific opportunity: [Job Link].\" Add one more short sentence mentioning my attached resume and my focus on building scalable systems.\n4. Paragraph 3: MUST consist of exactly these two sentences, word-for-word: \"Would you be open to referring me for the {{ $('Merge-company-Li').item.json.title }} position? Would you be willing to look at my attached resume to see if I am a strong fit?\"\n5. Output ONLY the raw email text. Stop generating immediately after Paragraph 3. Do not include a subject line, signature block, or conversational filler."
            }
          ]
        },
        "options": {}
      },
